# Agents Module: LangGraph Pipeline

The `lib/agents` module is the orchestration core of AuditSimple. It defines a LangGraph.js state machine that drives PII-scrubbed document text through a 7-node deterministic pipeline: `classify → extract_clauses → validate_clauses → benchmark → calculate_cost → generate_citations → synthesize`.

