### Nodes

#### [NEW] [nodes/classify.ts](file:///c:/Users/shahm/Desktop/Per.%20Proj/WealthSimple/AuditSimple/apps/web/lib/agents/nodes/classify.ts)
- No LLM retries in the node itself — `graph.ts` wraps it with `withRetry`
- Claude call: `temperature: 0.0`, `max_tokens: 200`, structured JSON output, 15s timeout
- Returns `ContractType` enum value + confidence
- If confidence < 0.6 → sets `UNKNOWN`, appends `AuditWarning`
- Returns `Partial<AgentState>`: `{ audit: { contractType }, currentNode: "classify" }`

#### [NEW] [nodes/extract-clauses.ts](file:///c:/Users/shahm/Desktop/Per.%20Proj/WealthSimple/AuditSimple/apps/web/lib/agents/nodes/extract-clauses.ts)
- Uses `EXTRACTION_TEMPLATES[state.audit.contractType]` from `lib/analysis`
- Claude call: `temperature: 0.0`, `max_tokens: 4000`, tool-use mode, 60s timeout
- Instructs LLM to return `null` for unfound clauses (per spec)
- Assigns `clauseId` (UUID v4), stub `SourceLocation` (page 1, full-page bounding box, verbatimText from rawValue)
- Returns `Partial<AgentState>`: `{ audit: { clauses } }`

#### [NEW] [nodes/validate-clauses.ts](file:///c:/Users/shahm/Desktop/Per.%20Proj/WealthSimple/AuditSimple/apps/web/lib/agents/nodes/validate-clauses.ts)
- **No LLM call**
- Imports `validateClause` from `lib/analysis`
- Runs all rules; on failure: downgrades `extractionConfidence` to `0.3`, appends `AuditWarning`
- Never removes clauses
- Returns `Partial<AgentState>`: `{ audit: { clauses: updatedClauses }, errors: [...warnings] }`

#### [NEW] [nodes/benchmark.ts](file:///c:/Users/shahm/Desktop/Per.%20Proj/WealthSimple/AuditSimple/apps/web/lib/agents/nodes/benchmark.ts)
- Imports `getBenchmarkForClause` from `lib/benchmarks`
- Imports `buildAuditIssue`, `assignSeverity` from `lib/analysis`
- For each clause with `numericValue != null`: calls `getBenchmarkForClause()`
- If lookup fails → appends warning, skips (never fails pipeline)
- Creates `AuditIssue` for UNFAVORABLE deviations; sorts issues by severity DESC
- Returns `Partial<AgentState>`: `{ audit: { issues } }`

#### [NEW] [nodes/calculate-cost.ts](file:///c:/Users/shahm/Desktop/Per.%20Proj/WealthSimple/AuditSimple/apps/web/lib/agents/nodes/calculate-cost.ts)
- **No LLM call**
- Imports `calculateCostOfLoyalty` from `lib/analysis`
- Extracts `termMonths` from clause with label `term_length` or `amortization_period` or `lease_term`
- Extracts `principal` from clause with label `principal_amount`
- Calls `calculateCostOfLoyalty(issues, termMonths, principal)`
- Returns `Partial<AgentState>`: `{ audit: { costOfLoyalty } }`

#### [NEW] [nodes/generate-citations.ts](file:///c:/Users/shahm/Desktop/Per.%20Proj/WealthSimple/AuditSimple/apps/web/lib/agents/nodes/generate-citations.ts)
- Imports `verifyCitations` from `lib/citations`
- Calls `verifyCitations(audit.clauses, pageTexts)`
- Clauses failing all 3 tiers: `extractionConfidence *= 0.4` (applied by the citations module itself)
- Merges citation warnings into state errors
- Returns `Partial<AgentState>`: `{ audit: { clauses: verifiedClauses }, errors: [...citationWarnings] }`

#### [NEW] [nodes/synthesize.ts](file:///c:/Users/shahm/Desktop/Per.%20Proj/WealthSimple/AuditSimple/apps/web/lib/agents/nodes/synthesize.ts)
- Imports `gateConfidence` from `lib/citations` to filter low-confidence clauses from summary context
- **Risk score is deterministic** (no LLM): uses `SEVERITY_WEIGHTS` formula from spec
- Claude call: `temperature: 0.3`, `max_tokens: 1000`, free text, 30s timeout
- System prompt constrains output to ≤300 words plain language
- Returns `Partial<AgentState>`: `{ audit: { executiveSummary, riskScore, status: COMPLETE, completedAt } }`

